{"tid":692323,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"各位ching點面對情緒勒索","createTime":"2018-06-06T14:08:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-06T16:18:49.000Z","uid":183963,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e7c3c9f3bf5b72adaf1df5fe0ec25d591f84eae3","tid":692323,"uid":183963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T14:08:56.000Z","msg":"發覺個個都鍾意情緒勒索人<br />\n尤其是屋企人同男女朋友<br />\n成日話我為你點點點付出都不求回報<br />\n而你又被佢哋講到一文不值、從來都唔緊張呢段關係<br />\n最攞命嘅係你真係好在乎/無得唔在乎同佢地嘅感情<br />\n所以你好傷 而且係被最親密嘅人傷到體無完膚<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b71161ab7b0774ee7fad1ec7d003edfd62850599","tid":692323,"uid":32746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T14:41:13.000Z","msg":"情緒勒索真係一隻手掌拍唔響<br />\n知道可能你好關顧身邊人既感受<br />\n但好多時都係睇你點回應人地既「勒索」<br />\n佢可以鬧你 你可以係好緊張內疚<br />\n但亦都可以當佢on99<br />\n可能你從小就習慣左呢種滿足人既pattern？<br />\n自己既內在同諗法都要靠自己<br />\n知道邊啲要求係合理 邊啲令你唔舒服<br />\nI know that feel bro<br />\n不過要改變都唔係一朝一夕<br />\n一齊加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6125004898d35e39d262a031d709918517b64f81","tid":692323,"uid":170365,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T15:09:23.000Z","msg":"學識企講 攤出嚟講<br />\n你開壞個頭 唔代表要繼續錯落去<br />\n肯同你傾嘅固然好事<br />\n唔肯嘅 都唔好輕易妥協<br />\n受罪嘅最終得你自己"},{"pid":"c88117d012ebd9aa0306d12a5511e21968f363a3","tid":692323,"uid":170229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T15:17:57.000Z","msg":"同著戇鳩無謂浪費時間"},{"pid":"2fb6772d891ea9ca113e8ff114ddb526ff4c21e5","tid":692323,"uid":125494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T15:20:22.000Z","msg":"我老豆老母最興用呢招<br />\n最後反撚左面，無聯絡半年以上"},{"pid":"99c87fa55cbab9d2843826441c39dded8ae303de","tid":692323,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T16:10:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  不如你教我點先唔再情緒勒索人"},{"pid":"bb7832fae2db76b2b7264ad7631b29f1dd00a1d8","tid":692323,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T16:18:49.000Z","msg":"俾d愛"}]}